{"word":"ἑδραῖος","slug":"ἑδραῖος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἑδραῖος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἕδρα'><el>ἕδρα</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>sitting, sedentary</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><el>ἑδραία ράχις</el> the horse's back <i>on which the rider sits</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>sitting fast, steady, steadfast</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}